metadata.name: Rinkeby Noun Mosaic
metadata.description:
Rinkeby is the main character of his own story.
 ⌐◨-◨
The Noun that started it all.
A representation of Rinkeby.
10k nouns with custom backgrounds to make the one and only Rinkeby. Featuring 2 custom nouns in the crowd,
"Mac Tonight" and "Marvin the burger Noun"

Format: PNG
Dimensions: 3200 x 3200 pixels

The collector will have the option of receiving a physical print of this artwork!
